{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":492,"text":"Six months ago, I got an email"},{"time":2673,"text":"from a man in Israel"},{"time":4080,"text":"who had read one of my books,"},{"time":5461,"text":"and the email said,"},{"time":6964,"text":"\"You don't know me,"},{"time":8971,"text":"but I'm your 12th cousin.\""},{"time":11443,"text":"And it said, \"I have a family tree"},{"time":13820,"text":"with 80,000 people on it, including you,"},{"time":17724,"text":"Karl Marx,"},{"time":18878,"text":"and several European aristocrats.\""},{"time":21478,"text":"Now I did not know what to make of this."},{"time":23880,"text":"Part of me was like, okay,"},{"time":26231,"text":"when's he going to ask me to wire"},{"time":28191,"text":"10,000 dollars to his Nigerian bank, right?"},{"time":31888,"text":"I also thought, 80,000 relatives,"},{"time":35576,"text":"do I want that?"},{"time":36854,"text":"I have enough trouble with some of the ones"},{"time":38672,"text":"I have already."},{"time":40109,"text":"And I won't name names, but you know who you are."},{"time":43775,"text":"But another part of me said, this is remarkable."},{"time":47024,"text":"Here I am alone in my office, but I'm not alone at all."},{"time":49760,"text":"I'm connected to 80,000 people around the world,"},{"time":53320,"text":"and that's four Madison Square Gardens"},{"time":56697,"text":"full of cousins."},{"time":58412,"text":"And some of them are going to be great,"},{"time":61349,"text":"and some of them are going to be irritating,"},{"time":63679,"text":"but they're all related to me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66495,"text":"So this email inspired me to dive into genealogy,"},{"time":70366,"text":"which I always thought was\na very staid and proper field,"},{"time":73766,"text":"but it turns out it's going through a fascinating"},{"time":76691,"text":"revolution, and a controversial one."},{"time":79184,"text":"Partly, this is because of DNA and genetic testing,"},{"time":82950,"text":"but partly, it's because of the Internet."},{"time":86900,"text":"There are sites that now take"},{"time":88660,"text":"the Wikipedia approach to family trees,"},{"time":91827,"text":"collaboration and crowdsourcing,"},{"time":94180,"text":"and what you do is,"},{"time":95358,"text":"you load your family tree on,"},{"time":98240,"text":"and then these sites search"},{"time":99720,"text":"to see if the A.J. Jacobs in your tree"},{"time":102402,"text":"is the same as the A.J. Jacobs in another tree,"},{"time":104882,"text":"and if it is, then you can combine,"},{"time":108115,"text":"and then you combine and combine and combine"},{"time":110010,"text":"until you get these massive,"},{"time":111911,"text":"mega-family trees"},{"time":113761,"text":"with thousands of people on them,"},{"time":116262,"text":"or even millions."},{"time":117677,"text":"I'm on something on Geni called"},{"time":120004,"text":"the world family tree,"},{"time":121930,"text":"which has no less than a jaw-dropping"},{"time":124487,"text":"75 million people."},{"time":128017,"text":"So that's 75 million people connected by blood"},{"time":131857,"text":"or marriage, sometimes both."},{"time":134337,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":136904,"text":"It's in all seven continents, including Antarctica."},{"time":141089,"text":"I'm on it. Many of you are on it,"},{"time":143466,"text":"whether you know it or not,"},{"time":145170,"text":"and you can see the links."},{"time":147634,"text":"Here's my cousin Gwyneth Paltrow."},{"time":152226,"text":"She has no idea I exist,"},{"time":154109,"text":"but we are officially cousins."},{"time":156800,"text":"We have just 17 links between us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":160996,"text":"And there's my cousin Barack Obama."},{"time":163689,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":164881,"text":"And he is my aunt's fifth great-aunt's husband's"},{"time":168506,"text":"father's wife's seventh great-nephew,"},{"time":172014,"text":"so practically my old brother."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177079,"text":"And my cousin, of course,"},{"time":178602,"text":"the actor Kevin Bacon --"},{"time":179919,"text":"(Laughter) â€”"},{"time":181571,"text":"who is my first cousin's twice removed's"},{"time":184535,"text":"wife's niece's husband's first cousin once removed's"},{"time":186927,"text":"niece's husband."},{"time":188137,"text":"So six degrees of Kevin Bacon,"},{"time":190272,"text":"plus or minus several degrees."}]},{"cues":[{"time":194391,"text":"Now, I'm not boasting, because all of you"},{"time":196772,"text":"have famous people and historical figures"},{"time":199000,"text":"in your tree, because we are all connected,"},{"time":202667,"text":"and 75 million may seem like a lot,"},{"time":205830,"text":"but in a few years, it's quite likely"},{"time":208556,"text":"we will have a family tree"},{"time":210069,"text":"with all, almost all, seven billion people on Earth."}]},{"cues":[{"time":214820,"text":"But does it really matter?"},{"time":216613,"text":"What's the importance?"},{"time":217955,"text":"And I do think it is important,"},{"time":219633,"text":"and I'll give you five reasons why, really quickly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":222111,"text":"First, it's got scientific value."},{"time":224931,"text":"This is an unprecedented history of the human race,"},{"time":228545,"text":"and it's giving us valuable data"},{"time":231976,"text":"about how diseases are inherited,"},{"time":234125,"text":"how people migrate,"},{"time":235993,"text":"and there's a team of scientists at MIT right now"},{"time":238913,"text":"studying the world family tree."}]},{"cues":[{"time":241593,"text":"Number two, it brings history alive."},{"time":244479,"text":"I found out I'm connected to Albert Einstein,"},{"time":247940,"text":"so I told my seven-year-old son that,"},{"time":250000,"text":"and he was totally engaged."},{"time":252846,"text":"Now Albert Einstein is not some dead white guy"},{"time":256213,"text":"with weird hair."},{"time":257423,"text":"He's Uncle Albert. (Laughter)"},{"time":261580,"text":"And my son wanted to know,"},{"time":263140,"text":"\"What did he say? What is E = MC squared?\""},{"time":265297,"text":"Also, it's not all good news."},{"time":267356,"text":"I found a link to Jeffrey Dahmer, the serial killer,"},{"time":271343,"text":"but I will say that's on my wife's side."},{"time":273960,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"},{"time":276648,"text":"So I want to make that clear. Sorry, honey."}]},{"cues":[{"time":279243,"text":"Number three, interconnectedness."},{"time":282132,"text":"We all come from the same ancestor,"},{"time":285495,"text":"and you don't have to believe\nthe literal Bible version,"},{"time":288063,"text":"but scientists talk about Y chromosomal Adam"},{"time":292151,"text":"and mitochondrial Eve,"},{"time":295004,"text":"and these were about 100,000 to 300,000 years ago."},{"time":298320,"text":"We all have a bit of their DNA in us."},{"time":301373,"text":"They are our great-great-great-great-great-great --"},{"time":304190,"text":"continue that for about 7,000 times --"},{"time":306930,"text":"grandparents,"},{"time":308745,"text":"and so that means we literally all are"},{"time":311391,"text":"biological cousins as well,"},{"time":313546,"text":"and estimates vary, but probably"},{"time":316102,"text":"the farthest cousin you have on Earth"},{"time":318804,"text":"is about a 50th cousin."},{"time":321259,"text":"Now, it's not just ancestors we share, descendants."},{"time":325440,"text":"If you have kids, and they have kids,"},{"time":328140,"text":"look how quickly the descendants accumulate."},{"time":331605,"text":"So in 10, 12 generations,"},{"time":333298,"text":"you're going to have thousands of offspring,"},{"time":335429,"text":"and millions of offspring."}]},{"cues":[{"time":336946,"text":"Number four, a kinder world."},{"time":338935,"text":"Now, I know that there are family feuds."},{"time":341424,"text":"I have three sons, so I see how they fight."},{"time":343719,"text":"But I think that there's also a human bias"},{"time":346385,"text":"to treat your family a little better than strangers."},{"time":348911,"text":"I think this tree is going to be bad news for bigots,"},{"time":352735,"text":"because they're going to have to realize"},{"time":356160,"text":"that they are cousins with thousands of people"},{"time":359770,"text":"in whatever ethnic group they happen"},{"time":361521,"text":"to have issues with,"},{"time":363783,"text":"and I think you look back at history,"},{"time":365668,"text":"and a lot of the terrible things\nwe've done to each other"},{"time":368669,"text":"is because one group thinks\nanother group is sub-human,"},{"time":371575,"text":"and you can't do that anymore."},{"time":373040,"text":"We're not just part of the same species."},{"time":374410,"text":"We're part of the same family."},{"time":376177,"text":"We share 99.9 percent of our DNA."}]},{"cues":[{"time":379813,"text":"Now the final one is number five,"},{"time":382114,"text":"a democratizing effect."},{"time":383793,"text":"Some genealogy has an elitist strain,"},{"time":387250,"text":"like people say, \"Oh, I'm descended"},{"time":389240,"text":"from Mary Queen of Scots"},{"time":390511,"text":"and you're not, so you cannot join my country club.\""},{"time":393718,"text":"But that's really going to be hard to do now,"},{"time":396659,"text":"because everyone is related."},{"time":398090,"text":"I'm descended from Mary Queen of Scots --"},{"time":400778,"text":"by marriage, but still."}]},{"cues":[{"time":404131,"text":"So it's really a fascinating time"},{"time":407627,"text":"in the history of family,"},{"time":409183,"text":"because it's changing so fast."},{"time":412690,"text":"There is gay marriage and sperm donors"},{"time":415265,"text":"and there's intermarriage\non an unprecedented scale,"},{"time":420185,"text":"and this makes some of my\nmore conservative cousins"},{"time":422411,"text":"a little nervous,"},{"time":424020,"text":"but I actually think it's a good thing."},{"time":425824,"text":"I think the more inclusive the idea of family is,"},{"time":429653,"text":"the better,"},{"time":430680,"text":"because then you have more potential caretakers,"},{"time":432784,"text":"and as my aunt's eighth cousin twice removed"},{"time":437099,"text":"Hillary Clinton says --"},{"time":439226,"text":"(Laughter) â€”"},{"time":440970,"text":"it takes a village."}]},{"cues":[{"time":442299,"text":"So I have all these hundreds and thousands,"},{"time":447562,"text":"millions of new cousins."},{"time":448680,"text":"I thought, what can I do with this information?"},{"time":451421,"text":"And that's when I decided,"},{"time":453277,"text":"why not throw a party?"},{"time":455516,"text":"So that's what I'm doing."},{"time":457752,"text":"And you're all invited."},{"time":460312,"text":"Next year, next summer,"},{"time":462210,"text":"I will be hosting what I hope is"},{"time":464141,"text":"the biggest and best family reunion in history."},{"time":468619,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":469651,"text":"Thank you. I want you there."},{"time":472053,"text":"I want you there."},{"time":473165,"text":"It's going to be at the New York Hall of Science,"},{"time":475639,"text":"which is a great venue,"},{"time":477921,"text":"but it's also on the site of the former World's Fair,"},{"time":481701,"text":"which is, I think, very appropriate,"},{"time":485346,"text":"because I see this as a family reunion"},{"time":487576,"text":"meets a world's fair."},{"time":488994,"text":"There's going to be exhibits and food, music."},{"time":491935,"text":"Paul McCartney is 11 steps away,"},{"time":494244,"text":"so I'm hoping he brings his guitar."},{"time":497844,"text":"He hasn't RSVP'd yet, but fingers crossed."},{"time":500579,"text":"And there is going to be a day of speakers,"},{"time":502970,"text":"of fascinating cousins."},{"time":504971,"text":"It's early, but I've already,"},{"time":506153,"text":"I've got some lined up."},{"time":508025,"text":"Cass Sunstein, my cousin who is perhaps"},{"time":510749,"text":"the most brilliant legal scholar, will be talking."},{"time":513137,"text":"He was a former member\nof the Obama administration."},{"time":516376,"text":"And on the other side of the political spectrum,"},{"time":519200,"text":"George H.W. Bush, number 41, the father,"},{"time":522332,"text":"he has agreed to participate,"},{"time":524187,"text":"and Nick Kroll, the comedian,"},{"time":526623,"text":"and Dr. Oz, and many more to come."},{"time":530122,"text":"And, of course, the most important is that you,"},{"time":534520,"text":"I want you guys there,"},{"time":536466,"text":"and I invite you to go to GlobalFamilyReunion.org"},{"time":539901,"text":"and figure out how you're on the family tree,"},{"time":542996,"text":"because these are big issues, family and tribe,"},{"time":547189,"text":"and I don't know all the answers,"},{"time":549907,"text":"but I have a lot of smart relatives,"},{"time":552756,"text":"including you guys,"},{"time":554337,"text":"so together, I think we can figure it out."},{"time":557604,"text":"Only together can we solve these big problems."},{"time":560259,"text":"So from cousin to cousin,"},{"time":562289,"text":"I thank you. I can't wait to see you."},{"time":564681,"text":"Goodbye."}]},{"cues":[{"time":566582,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}